            "title": null,
            "url": "__GHOST_URL__/articles/news/chevy-camaro-runs-out-of-road-in-australia/",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ". We’re just as shocked as you probably are to learn “most” police departments there had expressed at least some level of interest in getting ",
